synopsis: "The Homotopy Type Theory library"
description: """
To use the HoTT library, the following flags must be passed to coqc:
   -noinit -indices-matter

To use the HoTT library in a project, add the following to _CoqProject:
   -arg -noinit
   -arg -indices-matter
`
"""
